reviewText: Nothing can top Carlos Mencia's "tell it like it is" comedy. Laugh til your sides hurt, then laugh again. Great DVD.

reviewText: I have many Carlos Mencia DVD's. This one is good but definately not his best work. He is truly a comical genius in the ranks of Carlin and the like. Never any hesitation and humor that makes you think. Definately a dying breed.

reviewText: Joe Rogan has it all wrong. Carlos doesn't steal any more material than any other comedian. He's not Samsung, he can formulate his own ideas.
summary: Carlos is the funniest living comedian
Title: Carlos Mencia: New Territory

reviewText: Being a father has not changed Carlos - much.  He still uses awful language, and apparently, so does his school aged son - and he is okay with it. It is hard to imagine the worlds most popular, equal-opportunity racist as a father. Watch your back, Carlos - your son sounds like he is gonna follow close in your footsteps! And I can't wait for a Carlos and Company, as you and your son trade barbs.........it would be awesome!
Title: Carlos Mencia: New Territory

reviewText: I love the standup comedy of Carlos Mencia, not only is he funny but he is intelligently funny, most of his jokes actually make sense and you can tell that alot of thought are put into them. This is not his best work or standup I have ever seen but Mencia not at his best is still better than any other comedian any day in my opinion. Do not buy this if you get offended easily or do not have a sense of humor, because is definitely not for the easily offended. Mencia makes fun of every race, even his own, as a matter of fact he probably makes more fun of his own people than anyone else, so do not buy this if racial and ethnic jokes offend you because he makes fun of every race. If you love comedy and enjoy laughing you will enjoy Mencia. I recommend this dvd to everyone and if you do not know who Mencia is I would recommend that you first check out his standup dvd titled not for the easily offended, that one will have you laughing nonstop. Remember like Carlos says, If you're not laughing you're not living.
Title: Carlos Mencia: New Territory
